name: Chocolate-Strawberry
description: Chocolate genoise w/ chocolate whipped cream & strawberries. Topped with chocolate ganache drip, strawberries and chocolate truffles.

name: Classic Strawberry Cream
description: Vanilla sponge w/ whipped cream & strawberries. *Strawberry Whipcream available!

name: Devon Cream (Victorian Sponge)
description: A take on british-style scones w/ devon cream + raspberry jam, mixed with a classic victorian sponge cake.

name: Lemon Cake
description: Basically a Lemon Bundt Cake, but minus the Bundt Shape! Topped w/ candied lemons and lemon icing.

name: Milk Tea Coffee Crunch
description: Black tea sponge cake filled with milk tea flavored whipped cream and coffee crisp chocolate for extra texture. Masked with coffee flavored whipped ganache, and finished w/ whipped cream dollops.

name: Mint Chocolate
description: Chocolate genoise sponge-cake, mint-flavored whipped cream (stablized w/ a little bit of white chocolate), with dark chocolate ganache filling. Garnished with chocolate covered mint leaves, gold leaves, and a chocolate ring.

name: Peach Oolong (*Earl Grey Alternative)
description: Oolong flavored genoise sponge. Cooked white peach filling and oolong insert cream. Garnished with more white peaches, rose petals and jasmine petals. FROZEN PEACHES USED on off seasons!

name: Strawberry-Matcha
description: Matcha genoise sponge w/ strawberry whipped cream and strawberry slices. Royce-style matcha truffle chocolates (nama-chocolate) as added decoration!

name: Tea-Flavored Pound Cake
description: Matcha, Double Cream Earl Grey, Black Tea (Orange Pekoe), Various other black-tea flavors that I haven't tried yet!

name: Very Berry Custard
description: Vanilla sponge w/ a custard cream filling & home-made berry jam (raspberries, blueberries, blackberries, strawberries).
